ore, the cross correlation\npipeline reduces the detection threshold by a factor of 2 to 3 and\napproximately doubles the number of events in the REB, and thus, in the ISC\nbulletin for the North Atlantic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2016 09:05:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2017 16:38:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-11"}
